<br>
I constantly see these arguments about the Sleeper's Tomb and a constant referance is to guilds. What about the players, it is not a matter of taking this opportunity from guilds, it is from players. In one of those arguments someone put it perfectly, &quot;I payed for Velious just like many others, what gives YOU the right to alter my product?&quot;<br>
<br>
It is in hopes of ending these arguments and thus allowing future citizens of our great server the chance to visit this place in it's unaltered state, that I propose an agreement by EVERYONE here. It is simply thus, I will provide a statement below and you will repeat it in a single post with your name under it, full player name (in effect, your signature). It is not a matter of Fire and Fury or Resolution agreeing between themselves wether or not to wake the Sleeper, it is a PUBLIC matter. I do not want commentary, I do not want an argument, this post will not be turned into some bickering field for anyone. Simply copy the statement below, sign it, or do not post. I am hoping that the majority of the server can drop the crap and just agree to something like this. If anything there is more pride in letting the Sleeper live, and giving honor to our server and protecting our servers integrity as a whole, than waking it up and stealing what you had no right to take.<br>
<br>
The statement follows, again copy it in your post and sign it with your full player name (alts including if you wish)<br>
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
I hereby agree, that in order to preserve the sense of pride and integrity felt throughout all of Firione Vie; In order to allow all citizens of our Norrath to enjoy and profit from the Sleepers Tomb in it's current state, that I will not threaten, strive to kill, or even touch the final Warder in Kerafyms tomb. I will not awaken Kerafym nor take part in any attempt to wake him. I do this in order to preserve the world on Norrath that exists in our World of Firione Vie, I do this for all current citizens, and those that may come in the future.<br>
<br>
&lt;signature here&gt;<br>
<br>
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
I will be the first to sign this and I hope many will follow.<br>
